        <sharedstimulus id="assets/1242ffd863bb7ab878d9d/passage NEW 2.xml">
            <label key="29c4f2ba36d71a4f3138d40acdf34477">
                <text>Sinking Cities</text>
            </label>
            <label key="7fe6272b26f668a1d76dfd288ec27d54">
                <text>Coastal cities have a high risk of being impacted by rising sea levels. The risk is worsened if the land the cities are built on is sinking. This sinking is known as land subsidence (vertical downward movement of the Earth’s surface).</text>
            </label>
            <label key="dd1f45a25828b298d08255ac5bc7a89d">
                <text>Some of the most populated coastal cities are sinking faster than sea levels are rising.</text>
            </label>
